CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 9, 1958, pg. A15, reads: "Champagne Fountain at the Frogs' ball drew long-time Frog member Buddie Leftridge, Eunice and Ronald Pittman, Mary Short of New York and Orville Bates Jr. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait from left: Reverend LeRoy Patrick, unknown woman, Buddie Leftridge, Eunice Pittman, Ronald Pittman, Mary Short, and Orville Bates Jr., gathered around champagne fountain at FROGS event, Gateway Plaza
